title: UFYB 29: My Annual Review & Lessons Learned
itunes:title: My Annual Review & Lessons Learned
description:
This week, I decided to give you a behind-the-scenes look at my annual review and share the important lessons that I learned along the way. Join me to hear 5 most important things that I've learned from going through the process of growing my business 5x times and find out how you can apply these lessons in your own life and business/career.

Get full show notes and more information here: https://unfckyourbrain.com/29
